G4S runs three removal centres and until recently escorted detainees who were being deported.

More than half of all the complaints were made at Brook House, near Gatwick Airport in West Sussex, which holds convicted foreign criminals facing deportation.

G4S also runs Tinsley House, also near Gatwick Airport, and Dungavel House in South Lanarkshire.

